<h1 class="msg msg--info msg--highlight  align-center"><strong><span style="color: #e03e2d;">官方售价￥155.00元</span></strong></h1>
<h4 class="ng-star-inserted"><strong class="ng-star-inserted"><span class="ng-star-inserted">在安全与轻便之间，无需妥协</span></strong></h4>
<p class="ng-star-inserted"><span class="ng-star-inserted">在日常通勤、夜间慢跑或户外旅行中，个人安全始终是首要考量。作为全球公认的防护品牌，SABRE（沙豹）推出了突破性的</span><strong class="ng-star-inserted"><span class="ng-star-inserted">Mighty Discreet系列</span></strong><span class="ng-star-inserted">。这是同类产品中首款真正实现“极致微型”的强力辣椒喷雾，旨在为现代城市生活提供一种既隐蔽又强大的合法自卫方案。大盟安防防身装备</span></p>
<h4 class="ng-star-inserted"><strong class="ng-star-inserted"><span class="ng-star-inserted">一、 极致便携：隐形于方寸之间</span></strong></h4>
<p class="ng-star-inserted"><span class="ng-star-inserted">Mighty Discreet 的核心优势在于其革命性的体积设计。</span></p>
<ul class="ng-star-inserted">
<li class="ng-star-inserted">
<p class="ng-star-inserted"><strong class="ng-star-inserted"><span class="ng-star-inserted">体积缩小40%</span></strong><span class="ng-star-inserted">：相比传统的钥匙圈型喷雾，它彻底告别了臃肿感。</span></p>
</li>
<li class="ng-star-inserted">
<p class="ng-star-inserted"><strong class="ng-star-inserted"><span class="ng-star-inserted">全场景兼容</span></strong><span class="ng-star-inserted">：由于其纤细的身材，您可以轻松将其滑入紧身瑜伽裤的侧兜、精致的小手拿包，甚至是钥匙包内，实现真正的“隐形携带”。</span></p>
</li>
<li class="ng-star-inserted">
<p class="ng-star-inserted"><strong class="ng-star-inserted"><span class="ng-star-inserted">多功能挂扣</span></strong><span class="ng-star-inserted">：自带按扣式钥匙圈，可快速固定在背包拉链、挂绳或皮带环上，确保在紧急时刻能瞬间获取。</span></p>
</li>
</ul>
<h4 class="ng-star-inserted"><strong class="ng-star-inserted"><span class="ng-star-inserted">二、 核心威慑：小身材，大能量</span></strong></h4>
<p class="ng-star-inserted"><span class="ng-star-inserted">请不要被它的玲珑外表误导，SABRE Mighty Discreet 依然继承了沙豹家族的强悍基因：</span></p>
<ul class="ng-star-inserted">
<li class="ng-star-inserted">
<p class="ng-star-inserted"><strong class="ng-star-inserted"><span class="ng-star-inserted">HPLC实验室认证</span></strong><span class="ng-star-inserted">：SABRE拥有行业唯一的HPLC实验室，确保每一罐喷雾的辣素浓度始终如一，消除30%的效力偏差波动，为您提供确定性的防御效果。</span></p>
</li>
<li class="ng-star-inserted">
<p class="ng-star-inserted"><strong class="ng-star-inserted"><span class="ng-star-inserted">16次强劲喷射</span></strong><span class="ng-star-inserted">：足以应对多次潜在威胁，为逃离险境争取宝贵时间。</span></p>
</li>
<li class="ng-star-inserted">
<p class="ng-star-inserted"><strong class="ng-star-inserted"><span class="ng-star-inserted">12英尺（4米）射程</span></strong><span class="ng-star-inserted">：采用弹道式强劲水柱型（Stream），具备极强的抗风性能，可在安全距离内精准锁定目标，减少对自身的二次影响。</span></p>
</li>
</ul>
<h4 class="ng-star-inserted"><strong class="ng-star-inserted"><span class="ng-star-inserted">三、 专利设计：安全与取证并重</span></strong></h4>
<ul class="ng-star-inserted">
<li class="ng-star-inserted">
<p class="ng-star-inserted"><strong class="ng-star-inserted"><span class="ng-star-inserted">扭顶安全锁（Twist Top）</span></strong><span class="ng-star-inserted">：创新的安全装置能有效防止在口袋或包内发生意外喷漏。</span></p>
</li>
<li class="ng-star-inserted">
<p class="ng-star-inserted"><strong class="ng-star-inserted"><span class="ng-star-inserted">UV标记染料</span></strong><span class="ng-star-inserted">：喷雾配方中含有紫外线标记染料。一旦嫌疑人被喷射，即便其清洗掉表面污渍，警方仍可通过紫外线灯进行识别，大大提升了案件侦破率。</span></p>
</li>
</ul>
<h4 class="ng-star-inserted"><strong class="ng-star-inserted"><span class="ng-star-inserted">【详细规格参数】</span></strong></h4>
<ul class="ng-star-inserted">
<li class="ng-star-inserted">
<p class="ng-star-inserted"><strong class="ng-star-inserted"><span class="ng-star-inserted">产品产地</span></strong><span class="ng-star-inserted">：美国 (Made in USA)</span></p>
</li>
<li class="ng-star-inserted">
<p class="ng-star-inserted"><strong class="ng-star-inserted"><span class="ng-star-inserted">产品编号</span></strong><span class="ng-star-inserted">：MD-BK-02（经典黑）、MD-MT-02（薄荷绿）</span></p>
</li>
<li class="ng-star-inserted">
<p class="ng-star-inserted"><strong class="ng-star-inserted"><span class="ng-star-inserted">喷射型态</span></strong><span class="ng-star-inserted">：弹道式强劲水柱型（抗风、射流）</span></p>
</li>
<li class="ng-star-inserted">
<p class="ng-star-inserted"><strong class="ng-star-inserted"><span class="ng-star-inserted">喷射次数</span></strong><span class="ng-star-inserted">：间歇性喷射16次（约1秒/次）</span></p>
</li>
<li class="ng-star-inserted">
<p class="ng-star-inserted"><strong class="ng-star-inserted"><span class="ng-star-inserted">有效成分</span></strong><span class="ng-star-inserted">：1.33%辣椒素，10%辣椒油树脂（OC）</span></p>
</li>
<li class="ng-star-inserted">
<p class="ng-star-inserted"><strong class="ng-star-inserted"><span class="ng-star-inserted">保质期</span></strong><span class="ng-star-inserted">：4年</span></p>
</li>
<li class="ng-star-inserted">
<p class="ng-star-inserted"><strong class="ng-star-inserted"><span class="ng-star-inserted">认证标准</span></strong><span class="ng-star-inserted">：ISO 9001:2015、EPA认证、HPLC测试通过</span></p>
</li>
</ul>
<h4 class="ng-star-inserted"><strong class="ng-star-inserted"><span class="ng-star-inserted">【关于合法防御与隐私发货】</span></strong></h4>
<p class="ng-star-inserted"><span class="ng-star-inserted">我们深知个人防护产品的特殊性。本产品仅限用于正当防卫及紧急避险情况。</span></p>
<ul class="ng-star-inserted">
<li class="ng-star-inserted">
<p class="ng-star-inserted"><strong class="ng-star-inserted"><span class="ng-star-inserted">合法合规</span></strong><span class="ng-star-inserted">：倡导在法律框架内行使自卫权利，保护自身安全。</span></p>
</li>
<li class="ng-star-inserted">
<p class="ng-star-inserted"><strong class="ng-star-inserted"><span class="ng-star-inserted">隐私发货</span></strong><span class="ng-star-inserted">：我们严格保护客户隐私。所有订单均采用</span><strong class="ng-star-inserted"><span class="ng-star-inserted">中性加厚包装</span></strong><span class="ng-star-inserted">，面单不显示任何敏感词汇（如“防身”、“喷雾”等），确保配送全程隐秘，让您购买无忧。</span></p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr class="ng-star-inserted">
<p class="ng-star-inserted align-center"><strong class="ng-star-inserted"><span class="ng-star-inserted">立即配置SABRE Mighty Discreet，为您的出行增添一份从容与安全感。</span></strong></p>
            ]]>
        </content>
